  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Breakfast includes options like fresh croissants, pastries, bread, muesli with local honey, jams, fresh fruit and juices. There's also savoury options like cold cuts, cheeses, scrambled eggs, bacon and grilled sausages. Coffee lovers with enjoy the freshly prepared Italian espresso and cappuccino. It's served in the bright, modern breakfast room. </p>
<p><strong>Executive Delivery Bistrot </strong>is the hotel's dinner delivery service in collaboration with the restaurant La Ferramenta del Gusto Emiliano. Which means you can enjoy delicious food accompanied by a selection of wines. </p>
<p>Available between 7.30 - 10.30pm.</p>
<p><strong>Lounge Bar </strong>is the perfect place for aperitivo. The bright modern bar, located in the lobby, has comfortable seating and large tables. They serve a great selection of Piedmontese wines, liqueurs and Italian beers. It's also a nice place to head in the day for a coffee. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
  <cateringShortDescription></cateringShortDescription>
