  <facilityDescription><![CDATA[<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>Spa</strong></span></p>
<p>The hotels Vitamine Wellness centre is the perfect place to head after a day of sightseeing. There's a large heated whirlpool, relaxation area and a sauna. It's open from September to July 1st. </p>
<p>On the rooftop you'll find the heated hydro-massage pool, where you get amazing panoramic views of the city. There's a solarium up here with comfy lounge chairs, so you can just come up here to relax and enjoy the views. </p>
<p><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><strong>General Facilities</strong></span></p>
<ul>
<li><span style="text-decoration: underline;"></span>Free WiFi</li>
<li>24 hour gym</li>
<li>City bike rental (payable locally)</li>
<li>Tesla charging station</li>
<li>Garage (payable locally)</li>
</ul>]]></facilityDescription>
