  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Standard Rooms</strong> are about 21<span>m² and</span> sleep up to two adults. They're bright, spacious, modern and have a queen sized double bed or twin beds. They have space for a baby cot (available on request). All rooms have free WiFi, a minibar, desk, safe, TV, Sky TV channels, air conditioning and tea and coffee making facilities. Standard rooms that sleep up to three people are available for a supplement.  </p>
<p>Single rooms and double rooms for single use are available on request, please call to book. </p>]]></roomsDescription>
